h 🥰🥰\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eI started to think about an idea of Action. 🔧😄👨🏼‍💻\u003c/p\u003e\n\n","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Thomas Bnt","url":"https://dev.to/thomasbnt"},"datePublished":"2021-11-08T18:07:58Z","dateModified":"2021-11-08T18:07:58Z","url":"https://dev.to/thomasbnt/comment/1jh14","interactionStatistic":[{"@type":"InteractionCounter","interactionType":"https://schema.org/LikeAction","userInteractionCount":5}],"comment":[{"@type":"Comment","@id":"#comment-802462","text":"\u003cp\u003eHeck yes!!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Gracie Gregory (she/her)","url":"https://dev.to/graciegregory"},"datePublished":"2021-11-08T18:45:41Z","dateModified":"2021-11-08T18:45:41Z","url":"https://dev.to/graciegregory/comment/1jh1o","interactionStatistic":[{"@type":"InteractionCounter","interactionType":"https://schema.org/LikeAction","userInteractionCount":4}],"parentItem":{"@type":"Comment","@id":"#comment-802442"}},{"@type":"Comment","@id":"#comment-805702","text":"\u003cp\u003eUpdate of 15 November : I have nooo idea :c\u003c/p\u003e\n\n","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Thomas Bnt","url":"https://dev.to/thomasbnt"},"datePublished":"2021-11-15T17:51:17Z","dateModified":"2021-11-15T17:51:17Z","url":"https://dev.to/thomasbnt/comment/1jlme","interactionStatistic":[{"@type":"InteractionCounter","interactionType":"https://schema.org/LikeAction","userInteractionCount":1}],"parentItem":{"@type":"Comment","@id":"#comment-802442"}}]},{"@type":"Comment","@id":"#comment-803980","text":"\u003cp\u003eSo, if I add a pre-existing github action to my project and tweak it according to my needs..it will be a valid project? If not, can someone suggest me what exactly I have to do with pre-existing GitHub actions in order for it to be accepted?\u003c/p\u003e\n\n","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Utkarsh Maurya","url":"https://dev.to/utkarsh1311"},"datePublished":"2021-11-11T13:51:32Z","dateModified":"2021-11-11T13:51:32Z","url":"https://dev.to/utka